strings:
<voice_0x01001445><se_def>*: This is Tryan Gully!
Welcome, ha haargh!
<voice_0x01001446><se_low>King Trode: Urgh! I, I think a monster just spoke to me!

<voice_0x01001447><se_low>Yangus: COR BLI<endash>
Nah. I'm fed up wiv sayin' that old line now.
<voice_0x01001448><se_low>King Trode: You there! You're a monster but you don't fight or run away!? What business do you have being so welcoming!? Explain yourself!
<voice_0x01001449><se_def>*: Here in Tryan Gully, humans and elves and...
<voice_0x0100144B><se_def>*: So why would I run away when I see a human, haargh!?

<voice_0x0100144D><se_low>King Trode: ...I... Well, I never.
I had no idea such a place existed...

<voice_0x0100144E><se_low>King Trode: Of course! You know what this means!
I can wander about without causing a stir!
It's a veritable paradise!

<voice_0x0100144F><se_low>King Trode: Well, what are we waiting for!?
Come on! Follow me!
